description: Highest minimal norm of n-dimensional unimodular lattice.
references: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, A new upper bound for the minimum of an integral lattice of determinant one, Bull. Amer. Math. Soc., 23 (1990), 383-387.
J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. xxiv.
N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
extensions: The entries continue: 3 or 4, 3 or 4, 4, 3 or 4, 3 or 4, 3 or 4, 4 (at dim 40).
